    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Disaster Blaster》是一款类Roguelite自动化卡牌游戏，你将扮演一位精神状态堪忧的科学家，试图打造宇宙中最夸张的武器。设计你的武器射击机制，在一片不幸星球的银河中对抗成群的外星敌人，释放混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更新新增内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主播模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主播模式（测试版）是一种全新的游戏模式，<strong>可以将 Disaster Blaster 直接连接到你的直播中</strong>，让你的观众成为混乱的一部分。观众可以通过聊天和其他直播事件与游戏互动，以完全不可预测的方式影响游戏过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主播模式（测试版）支持<strong>Twitch 和 TikTok Live</strong>！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>固定系统（Pin）</strong><br>想要更好地控制构建？通过固定系统，你可以预设最多3张关键卡牌，提高它们在游戏中出现的几率。非常适合从一开始就策划毁灭性连击！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的爆破枪...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的武器中添加和更换卡牌，随着效果按顺序应用于下一发射击。提升伤害、增加射速，将子弹变为燃烧和反弹的弹药！创造惊人的连击，见证你的作品进化并变成不可战胜的力量！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/bdbb0244761711054b5e9688071f6f74.poster.avif?t=1752588836\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/bdbb0244761711054b5e9688071f6f74.webm?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/bdbb0244761711054b5e9688071f6f74.mp4?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...摧毁其他一切</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在由外星人领导的虚拟征服任务中测试你的武器，该外星人将面对无尽的敌人潮，直到整颗星球被摧毁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/5960a4eab8a2dd34f756716e31bfcd15.poster.avif?t=1752588836\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/5960a4eab8a2dd34f756716e31bfcd15.webm?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/5960a4eab8a2dd34f756716e31bfcd15.mp4?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现新星球和外星种族</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索新星球，与具有独特能力的本土外星种族交锋。解锁这些外星种族，使其成为你在未来游戏中测试武器的助手，利用他们的力量创造更具动态的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/ef54e08e6b83d6c7ae7f8fc650c2c914.poster.avif?t=1752588836\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/ef54e08e6b83d6c7ae7f8fc650c2c914.webm?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/ef54e08e6b83d6c7ae7f8fc650c2c914.mp4?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁数十种不同的卡牌，结合外星能力以最大化你的攻击潜力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/241e4a9747546655df01c698d2e45879.poster.avif?t=1752588836\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/241e4a9747546655df01c698d2e45879.webm?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194600/extras/241e4a9747546655df01c698d2e45879.mp4?t=1752588836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快节奏、多样化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受激烈的15分钟对战，以及无尽的自定义可能性。每一局都是不同的体验！</p>",
